&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our customers come from all walks of life and so do we. We hire great people from a wide variety of backgrounds, not just because it&#39;s the right thing to do, but because it makes our company stronger. If you share our values and our enthusiasm for small businesses, you will find a home at Gusto.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
